      <title>如何利用FRP搭建本地内网穿透</title>
      <link href="/2024/05/05/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8FRP%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F/"/>
      <url>/2024/05/05/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8FRP%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p><strong><span style='color:white;background:black;'>  2024.5.5 </span> <span style='color:white;'><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mT421X7xi/">视频版教程</a></span></strong></p><p>这篇文件会教大家如何从0开始搭建TCP内网穿透</p><p>接下来让我们开始吧</p><hr><h2 id="一·准备"><a href="#一·准备" class="headerlink" title="一·准备"></a>一·准备</h2><p>1.首先下载FRP<a href="https://github.com/fatedier/frp?tab=readme-ov-file#about-v2">GitHub</a>)←←windows版本和Linux版本都在这,最新版也在这里</p><p> 我这里用0.47.0演示</p><p> <a href="https://wwp.lanzouq.com/iJlsY1xql4vc">蓝奏云←windows版本</a>,密码:9p41</p><p> <a href="https://wwp.lanzouq.com/ijffD1xql53a">蓝奏云←Linux版本</a>,密码:6bvs</p><p>2.准备一台云服务器,我这里用阿里云来演示(如果是新用户可以白嫖一台的！！！)</p><p> 点击实例进入并找到 <font color='IndianRed'>重置密码</font></p><img src="https://www.ethanaxe.online/img/FRPmd/阿里实例.png" width="80%" height="95%"  /><p>3.下载<a href="https://www.hostbuf.com/t/988.html">FinalShell</a>)</p><p> 打开FinalShell,新建链接</p><img src="https://www.ethanaxe.online/img/FRPmd/fs新建链接.png" width="50%" height="50%"  /><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">名称:随意</span><br><span class="line">主机填写你服务器的ip,端口:22</span><br><span class="line">用户名:root</span><br><span class="line">密码:刚才设置的密码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 然后点击确定,链接成功</p><h2 id="二·开始配置"><a href="#二·开始配置" class="headerlink" title="二·开始配置"></a>二·开始配置</h2><p>1.打开你的云服务器点击安全组,配置端口</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">目的:7000 你的frp远程端口</span><br><span class="line">源: 填写0.0.0.0/0</span><br><span class="line">目的:xxxxx 你的远程端口</span><br><span class="line">源: 填写0.0.0.0/0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.打开<span style='color:white;background:Gray;'> frp-windows </span></p><p> 点击frpc.ini,输入</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[common]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server_addr</span> = xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx <span class="comment">#你的服务器公网ip</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server_port</span> = <span class="number">7000</span> <span class="comment">#默认7000就行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">token</span> = xxxxx <span class="comment">#你的链接密码不是远程桌面密码</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[xxx]</span> <span class="comment">#自定义名字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type</span> = tcp <span class="comment">#链接方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_ip</span> = <span class="number">127.0</span>.<span class="number">0.1</span> <span class="comment">#本地ip</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_port</span> = xxxxx <span class="comment">#本地端口</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">remote_port</span> = <span class="number">25566</span> <span class="comment">#远程端口</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.打开<span style='color:white;background:Gray;'> frp-Linux </span></p><p> 点击frps.ini,输入</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[common]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">bind_port</span> = <span class="number">7000</span> <span class="comment">#默认7000就行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">token</span> = xxxxx <span class="comment">#刚才在frpc设置的密码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.在FinalShell,依次输入代码</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /你的frp存放目录</span><br><span class="line">./frps <span class="literal">-c</span> ./frps.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 反馈 <span style='color:white;background:SteelBlue;'> frps started successfully </span> 就成功弄好frps了</p><p>5.在本地frp文件夹 <font color='IndianRed'>Shift+右键</font> 点击在终端中打开,输入代码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./frpc -c ./frpc.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 反馈<span style='color:white;background:SteelBlue;'> start proxy success </span>就完成了</p><h2 id="三·测试是否完成"><a href="#三·测试是否完成" class="headerlink" title="三·测试是否完成"></a>三·测试是否完成</h2><p>启动我的世界服务器,连接ip为:<font color='DeepSkyBlue'>你的服务器IP:你的远程端口</font></p><p>测试完成,开服！！</p>]]></content>
      
      
